  ## setTXPower

  Sets the BLE transmit power for the Ollie.

  Uses more battery, but gives longer range


  ### Params


  - **level** (<code>Number</code>) power to set


  - **callback** (<code>Function</code>) function to call when done


  ### Returns

  - (<code>undefined</code>)

  * * *

  ## setRGB

  Sets the RGB color of Ollie's built-in LED


  ### Params


  - **color** (<code>Number</code>) color value to set


  - **persist** (<code>Boolean</code>) whether color should persist through power cycles


  - **callback** (<code>Function</code>) function to call when done


  ### Returns

  - (<code>undefined</code>)

