  ## roll

  Tells Ollie to roll in a particular speed and heading


  ### Params


  - **speed** (<code>Number</code>) speed to roll at


  - **heading** (<code>Number</code>) heading to roll at


  - **state** (<code>Number</code>) roll state value


  - **callback** (<code>Function</code>) function to call when done


  ### Returns

  - (<code>undefined</code>)

